			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is for the barbarian shawman.  This guid is more of an addon to the barbarian warrior guid.  The shawman is better than the warrior because he  can heal and cast spells, but is still strong.  Go to your guild and get your spells memorize them and make hot buttons.  Then go money hunting.  Stay near the groups of people and heal one of them if they are in trouble.  They help you when your getting slaughtered by a group of goblins.  The skelitons are easy to kill and sometimes have swords.  Thier bones are worth keeping and selling. I suggest finding a backpack.  They are very usefull since you don't have to make as many trips back to the merchants.  Get yourself a nice mace and sheild and you will do fine against a polorbearcub (one).<BR>
Do not let the gremlins gang up on you.  Fishing is a very good cash flow but boring.  Use your inner fire spell always before fighting.  You can eventually talor and Blacksmith but I haven't been bored enough to do that yet.  Never ever run from an opponet they will just kill you from the back and chase you.
				</font>
			</td>

