				Ya know, there's all this stuff about how the Shamen and warriors are better than each other but what about the rouge.  As far as I'm conserned... ROUGES ROCK!  They have backstab, an attack that does TRIPLE DIGIT damage.  They have pick pocket.  It's hard to steal at low levels, but at high ones, you can get a nice platnum or two. :) Also, my level seven rouge can tank.  It has 170 hitpoints and when I tank, I have never died once.  In conclusion I have had better luck as a barbarian rouge than as a barbarian warrior or shamen.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
